# Data Type
* Logical
```{R}
  v <- 2L
  print(class(v))
```
* Numeric
```{r}
  v <- 23.5
  print(class(v))
```
* Integer
```{r}
  v <- 2L
  print(class(v))
```
* Complex
```{r}

  v <- 2+5i
  print(class(v))
```
* Character
```{r}
  v <- "TRUE"
  print(class(v))

```
* Raw
```{r}
  v <- charToRaw("Hello")
  print(class(v))
```
